text.section:
A claim for the loss shall:
Be based on an act or omission that occurs in the provision of funeral pre-need services by:
A licensed mortician;
A licensed funeral director;
A licensed apprentice mortician;
A licensed apprentice funeral director; or
An unlicensed employee of a licensed funeral establishment;
Involve a transaction that relates to pre-need funeral planning that occurred in the State; and
Be based on an act or omission:
In which pre-need money is obtained from a person by theft, embezzlement, false pretenses, or forgery; or
That constitutes fraud or misrepresentation.
